{"tid":1801038,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民望年度總結 林鄭大跌30分 近六成人不信港府中央","createTime":"2019-12-28T10:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T11:07:05.000Z","uid":53062,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8241bc51d048a2472743632884c75c26b38bbf90","tid":1801038,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:45:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191228/s00001/1577471020641/%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%90-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%8C30%E5%88%86-%E8%BF%91%E5%85%AD%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E4%BF%A1%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191228%2Fs00001%2F1577471020641%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%259C%259B%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%2590-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B7%258C30%25E5%2588%2586-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNQ2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=28fdc0df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191228%2Fs00001%2F1577471020641%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%259C%259B%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%2590-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B7%258C30%25E5%2588%2586-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE&h=a5f41de0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191228/s00001/1577471020641/%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%90-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%8C30%E5%88%86-%E8%BF%91%E5%85%AD%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E4%BF%A1%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20191228/s00006/d6112e45ee6208045e7e6024e1be52bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20191228%2Fs00006%2Fd6112e45ee6208045e7e6024e1be52bf.jpg&h=57b2dce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】中文大學香港亞太研究所為特首林鄭月娥及政府作2019年民望總結。林太民調評分較一年前下滑30分，至22.2分（100分滿分）；市民對香港政府原本是信任多於不信任，但反修例風暴後，演變成近六成人不信香港政府及北京中央政府。<br />\n<br />\n亞太研究所公布今年12月份民調結果，調查在本月中訪問708名18歲或以上市民。民調顯示，林鄭月娥本月評分22.2，較11月微跌0.2分，變化不大。但亞太研究所指出，對比一年前的52.7分，林鄭今年評分跌幅顯著。<br />\n<br />\n民調分析顯示，51歲或以上受訪者對林鄭平均評分為25.1，31至50歲是20.6，30歲或以下是11.6；<span style=\"color: red;\">學歷愈高者對林鄭評分愈低。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3名司長方面，早前倒地傷手的律政司長鄭若驊評分持續下跌，由去年12月的39.3分，跌至本月的15.9分，在3名司長中評分最低。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊15.9分 3司中最低<br />\n對港府滿意度方面，本月表示不滿意的受訪者佔69.6％，滿意是10.6％，表示普通/一半半者佔19.4％。<br />\n<br />\n本月調查中，13.7%受訪者表示信任北京中央政府，不信任的則有58.4%。綜觀全年，市民對中央政府的不信任度由3月起持續增加，至12月才輕微回落不足1個百分點。對港府信任度方面，一年前對港府表示信任的有30.6％、不信任是25.7％；4月起民情逆轉，本月表示不信任港府的有59%，信任港府的為14.8％，後者比去年同期少一半。"},{"pid":"322bf7b8e4bb191bb42f31b6e3cf144b44cd1bf7","tid":1801038,"uid":37413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:51:57.000Z","msg":"仲有咁過分，全部最少單位數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fe542d9670e7d291c1a9e9c46231e1355a351a","tid":1801038,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:53:41.000Z","msg":"點止六成"},{"pid":"cf46973c45192d5aa6707c1dd147d8f7c217fcc3","tid":1801038,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c59e8a0a99f04525608cff4636dbae84093d9b03","tid":1801038,"uid":259246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:57:21.000Z","msg":"香港人真係易管<br />\n上年竟然咁高分"},{"pid":"fe587005639ba6d635d5c6258e9bec64a0a37e55","tid":1801038,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:57:42.000Z","msg":"普通一